## Configuration

This plugin declares an install-time config schema (see `plugin.yaml`'s
`config:` block). Operators see a form in the enroll wizard with two
fields:

- `greeting` — the word prefixed before the name (default `Hello`)
- `shout` — uppercase the output (default `false`)

See [docs/plugins/CONFIG_AUTHORING.md](https://github.com/WangYihang/Platypus/blob/main/docs/plugins/CONFIG_AUTHORING.md)
for the deeper guide on adding more fields, marking secrets, and
schema versioning.
